{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12/comments/36107093.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12#comment-36107093"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 12, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{bc79acda-fe93-46b4-96a4-f1603142a10a}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo_experimental", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo_experimental", "uuid": "{bc79acda-fe93-46b4-96a4-f1603142a10a}"}, "title": "Changes to simulation time to support pausing"}, "content": {"raw": "When not paused `Manager::UpdateSystems()` adds the time step to the current simulation time and updates the systems. When paused `Manager::UpdateSystems()` updates the systems, but the current simulation time is unchanged. A convenience method `bool Manager::IsPaused()` could be added for systems to check. This allows GUI / rendering / movement systems to update when paused, while systems like the physics system should check if the simulation is paused and skip the update.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>When not paused <code>Manager::UpdateSystems()</code> adds the time step to the current simulation time and updates the systems. When paused <code>Manager::UpdateSystems()</code> updates the systems, but the current simulation time is unchanged. A convenience method <code>bool Manager::IsPaused()</code> could be added for systems to check. This allows GUI / rendering / movement systems to update when paused, while systems like the physics system should check if the simulation is paused and skip the update.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-04-20T18:35:29.578919+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Shane Loretz", "uuid": "{656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22/c7a1ebf5-cade-4115-9f26-9d3facb776db/128"}}, "nickname": "Shane Loretz", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 36107093}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12/comments/36302391.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12#comment-36302391"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/12.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 12, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_experimental.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{bc79acda-fe93-46b4-96a4-f1603142a10a}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo_experimental", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo_experimental", "uuid": "{bc79acda-fe93-46b4-96a4-f1603142a10a}"}, "title": "Changes to simulation time to support pausing"}, "content": {"raw": "Passing on this in favor pull request #19. Related to #8", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Passing on this in favor <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental/pull-requests/19/add-simulationtime-getter-setter-and\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #19</a>. Related to <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo_experimental/issues/8/make-it-easy-for-a-system-to-know-current\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Make it easy for a system to know current simulation time\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#8</s></a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-04-25T20:21:51.149750+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Shane Loretz", "uuid": "{656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b